    "username": "emollick",
    "nickname": "Ethan Mollick",
    "text": "A fundamental problem with extending Codex/Cowork/Code to all knowledge work is that they remain very \"software-brained\" where the end result (the software) is what is important &amp; that code serves as a source of truth.\n\nFor a lot of other knowledge work, the process is at least",
