    "username": "emollick",
    "nickname": "Ethan Mollick",
    "text": "This is aside from the other key \"software brain\" problems of Codex and Code: dividing all work into front-end and back-end design, solving for the general case in a repeatable way, not testing or exploring  idea spaces, testing for technical correctness but not other aspects...",
